        {
            "id": 6009112,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 特斯拉(TSLA-US)大跌5.07%，報315.21美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>特斯拉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>)截至台北時間05日21:39股價下跌16.84美元，報315.21美元，跌幅5.07%，成交量17,332,966（股），盤中最高價324.55美元、最低價315.20美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.7%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>特斯拉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-6.96%</li> <li>近 1 月：+15.61%</li> <li>近 3 月：+22.06%</li> <li>近 6 月：-7.23%</li> <li>今年以來：-17.78%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6009112",
